text: Laufen or Laufen an der Salzach (Bavarian: Laffa an da Soizach) is a town in Berchtesgadener Land, a district (Landkreis) in Upper Bavaria. == Sister towns and cities == Laufen, Germany is twinned with: * Laufen, Switzerland == References == == Other websites == * Category:Berchtesgadener Land
title: Laufen, Germany
